creator: HRDEV Tech Solutions
descriptionHtml:
Lucky number prediction is the third-party APIs-based prediction of the horoscope, It predicts the user lucky number, lucky color, day summary and also tells users zodiac sign based on the username and dob.

Users can also predict for the day before and day after. And also user can predict lucky number based on his/her zodiac sign.
Zodiac Signs are based on Indian Astrology which has a total of 12 signs.

If user don't know his/her zodiac sign this app will automatically predict based on the username and date of birth.

It also predicts the lottery numbers of famous U.S lottery game (Lotto and EuroMillions) . It generates the max possibility of numbers which may come in lottery (note : this app doesn't encourage anyone for playing or buying any lottery ticket for more details please check our terms and conditions screen in app).

It is a pure safe app no user data is stored anywhere, whatever data is asked for prediction is stored in the user phone itself which can be easily removed by the user at any time.

Our aim is to provide this information to all users for free.
